{"tid":2333590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎｜政府專家警告最後關頭或須戒嚴抗疫 疫情惡化應限商舖營業","createTime":"2020-12-20T14:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T02:19:44.000Z","uid":80564,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7ff4b379e9d70a3d0a2abee41d9a4bfdae3e5001","tid":2333590,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:12:49.000Z","msg":"最後關頭或須居家令<br />\n<br />\n他預計學校恢復面授課程或要等新年後再視乎疫情走勢決定；面對大批屋苑群組爆發，屋宇署要盡快為住戶檢查喉管，解決結構性問題，但難以評估目前進度是否太慢，因為無法預計哪個屋苑會爆疫，本港居住密度高，可能太多個案「做唔切」。當局可以考慮要求再爆發的外傭群組納入定期強制檢測。<br />\n許承認，再收緊社交措施或令市民轉去私人地方聚會，但私人地方很難監察，只能盡量呼籲市民避免。他指如果用盡措施市民都不能配合，最後關頭或要考慮居家令，仿傚澳洲墨爾本接近戒嚴，<span class=\"red\">只讓市民每天數小時出去運動，其餘時間在家。<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJAXqFq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJAXqFq.gif&h=21f7cb5b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201220/KQ3RJVSPSFC4TKO7QDJ4EN6ATI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2Ka1MYKLPZvxl6UPOr5BcRR6LAL269wSNeHYfFQ5YDRS81C6owm_SnDKo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201220%2FKQ3RJVSPSFC4TKO7QDJ4EN6ATI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2Ka1MYKLPZvxl6UPOr5BcRR6LAL269wSNeHYfFQ5YDRS81C6owm_SnDKo&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIYMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=2359ec0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201220%2FKQ3RJVSPSFC4TKO7QDJ4EN6ATI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2Ka1MYKLPZvxl6UPOr5BcRR6LAL269wSNeHYfFQ5YDRS81C6owm_SnDKo&h=4f881977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201220/KQ3RJVSPSFC4TKO7QDJ4EN6ATI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp